This creates a thin sage-to-purple gradient bar at the top of canvas cards. It is visible above the `CanvasPreview` component since the pseudo-element has `z-index: 2`. The gradient subtly ties into the remix button's purple accent, creating visual cohesion between the card type indicator and the remix action.

